Map made by gangie!
Idea by Mathias<3<3
-----------------------
This map is a remake of the famous bussesfrom hell, exept, here we are driving in Ford GT500 and Helicopters!
The GT's drives like the busses, exept, that it's driving a bit diffrent, and has a Horn, when U click "fire" :D
The Heli's can throw a little red bomb, on "attack2"/right mouse button, and goes up in the air on "fire" ! :D
That means, that there can be 4 T's 2 for the cars and 2 for the Helicopters! :D

The CT's have to survive in 3 minuts to survive!

Thx to Natalya[AF]
